config.script:
#Get File Path To has been dropped
	#self.view.custom.filePath = event['name']
	
	#Process File
	system.perspective.print("Reading File......")
	fileBytes = event.file.getBytes()
	system.perspective.print("Process File......")
	data = Standard.Utilities.Excel.ExcelToList(bytesIn = fileBytes,hasHeaders = True)
	system.perspective.print("Process File......Done!")
	#Add a unique key to assist with data row identification
	system.perspective.print(str(len(data)))
	i=1
	for row in data:
		row['localID'] = i
		i = i+1
	self.custom.RawData = data

#Script to create all tags imported into Raw Data Table
	tagData = self.getSibling("Tag Summary").props.data
	tableColumnMapping = self.view.custom.ColumnParameterMapping
	#Constants
	collisionPolicy = self.parent.getChild("Collision Policy").getChild("Dropdown").props.value
	basePath = self.parent.getChild("Base Folder Path").getChild("TextField").props.text
	#Control Module Constants
	historyModelPathPrefix = self.parent.getChild("HistoryModelPathPrefix").getChild("value").props.text
	historyStorageProvider = self.parent.getChild("HistoryStorageProvider").getChild("value").props.text
	opcPath = self.parent.getChild("OPCPath").getChild("value").props.text
	opcServerName = self.parent.getChild("OPCServerName").getChild("value").props.text
	parentTagProviderFolderPath = self.parent.getChild("ParentTagProviderFolderPath").getChild("value").props.text

	#Control Module Mapping
	controlModuleMapping = self.view.custom.ControlModuleMapping
	controlModulePaths = self.view.custom.ControlModulePaths
	
	tagsCreated = []		
	# Iterate through the imported tagData
	for row in tagData:
		#Generate the base tag path
		tagPathString = row["IgnitionTagPath"]
		if tagPathString == "":
			continue
		elif tagPathString is None:
			continue
		tagPathArray = tagPathString.rsplit("/",1)
		folderPath = tagPathArray[0]
		tagName = tagPathArray[1]
		baseTagPath = basePath + folderPath	
		#Tag Properties
		tagType = "UdtInstance"
		#Find Control Module Type
		controlModuleType = row[tableColumnMapping["ControlModule"]]
		controlModuleUDTPath = ""
		for controlModuleKey in controlModuleMapping:
			controlModuleName = controlModuleMapping[controlModuleKey]
			if controlModuleName == controlModuleType:
				controlModuleUDTPath = controlModulePaths[controlModuleKey]
				break
		if controlModuleUDTPath == "":
			continue
		params = {
					  "HistoryModelPathPrefix":historyModelPathPrefix,
					  "HistoryStorageProvider":historyStorageProvider,
					  "OPCPath":opcPath,
					  "OPCServerName":opcServerName,
					  "ParentTagProviderFolderPath":parentTagProviderFolderPath,
					  "Description":""
							}		
		#Add Control Module Specific Parameters
		if controlModuleKey == "AI":
			#Engineering Units
			engUnits = ""
			if tableColumnMapping["EngUnits"] in row:
				engUnits = row[tableColumnMapping["EngUnits"]]		
			
			params["EngUnits"] = engUnits	
					
			#Instrument Type
			IntrumentType = ""
			if tableColumnMapping["InstrumentType"] in row:
				IntrumentType = row[tableColumnMapping["InstrumentType"]]			
			params["InstrumentType"] = IntrumentType		
			
		elif controlModuleKey == "Controller":
			outputEngUnits = ""
			processVariableEngUnits = ""
			params["OuputEngUnits"] = outputEngUnits	
			params["ProcessVariableEngUnits"] = processVariableEngUnits
			
		elif controlModuleKey == "DI":
			labelActive = "Active"
			labelPassive = "Passive"
		
			params["LabelActive"] = labelActive	
			params["LabelPassive"] = labelPassive
		
		elif controlModuleKey == "Totaliser":
			#Engineering Units
			engUnits = ""
			if tableColumnMapping["EngUnits"] in row:
				engUnits = row[tableColumnMapping["EngUnits"]]			
			params["EngUnits"] = engUnits
						
		tag = {
					"name": tagName,         
					"typeId" : controlModuleUDTPath,
					"tagType" : tagType
					,"parameters" : params
			   }
		tagsCreated.append(tag)
		system.tag.configure(baseTagPath, [tag], collisionPolicy)		
	self.custom.data = tagsCreated
